OL,3,CHorizon inquiry: Post Office
OL,4,Cinvestigator 'uncomfortable' with
OL,5,Csearching Newcastle victim's home
OL,7,FA former Post Office investigator has
OL,8,Ftold the Horizon inquiry that he was
OL,9,F"uncomfortable" with searching
OL,10,Fsubpostmasters homes but did so
OL,11,Fbecause it was part of the job.
OL,13,FRobert Daily was involved in the
OL,14,Fcriminal investigations for wrongly
OL,15,Fconvicted subpostmasters including
OL,16,FPeter Holmes who ran a branch in the
OL,17,FJesmond area of Newcastle.
