OL,7,FMr Holmes was wrongly found to have
OL,8,Fstolen #46,000 from his branch and was
OL,9,Fhanded a community order and a curfew.
OL,10,FHe died from a brain tumour in 2015,
OL,11,Fsix years before his conviction was
OL,12,Fquashed.
OL,14,FHis fight has been taken up by his
OL,15,Fwife Marion, who is still yet to
OL,16,Freceive any compensation for what they
OL,17,Fwent through.
