OL,7,FAt the inquiry into the scandal on
OL,8,FTuesday, Mr Daily was asked about his
OL,9,Finvestigation into Mr Holmes, denying
OL,10,Fany personal responsibility for what
OL,11,Fhappened to him.
OL,13,FHe was asked by Christopher Jacobs, a
OL,14,Flegal representative for
OL,15,Fsubpostmasters including Mr Holmes'
OL,16,Fwidow Marion, about his claim that he
OL,17,Fdid not know about issues with Horizon
OL,18,Fwhile investigating the Newcastle
OL,19,Fsubpostmaster.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/14
