OL,5,Csearching Newcastle victim's home
OL,7,FHe replied: "I can only tell you that
OL,8,Fwhen Mr Holmes brought up Horizon in
OL,9,Fan interview with myself, from what I
OL,10,Frecall, that's the first time I heard
OL,11,Fsomeone bring it up in an interview.
OL,13,F"I wasn't aware of all the other cases
OL,14,Fthat were going ahead, I don't even
OL,15,Fknow half of these people, or most, or
OL,16,Fall of these people that have been
OL,17,Fmentioned here or in this inquiry. It
OL,18,Fwas never fed down to us."
