OL,7,FHe later added: "I can't recall when
OL,8,Fthe Post Office started telling us
OL,9,Fthere were issues with Horizon ` I
OL,10,Fcouldn't honestly give you the first
OL,11,Fdate I was aware of it."
OL,13,FAddressing the searches conducted at
OL,14,FMr Holmes' address, Mr Jacobs said:
OL,15,F"Was it normal to go into people's
OL,16,Fhomes, go into their bedrooms and
OL,17,Ftheir drawers and take out statements
OL,18,Ffrom banks before a postmaster or
OL,19,Fassistant had been interviewed?"
