OL,7,FMr Daily replied: "If you're asking me
OL,8,Fif I was comfortable doing that, no I
OL,9,Fwasn't comfortable but it was part of
OL,10,Fthe job and it was done voluntarily."
OL,12,FHe said it was "expected" that
OL,13,Finvestigators would carry out a search
OL,14,Ffirst before conducting an interview.
