OL,7,FMr Daily replied: "Not at the time,
OL,8,Fsir."
OL,10,FEarlier on Tuesday, Mr Daily told the
OL,11,Finquiry that recovery targets were
OL,12,F"unfair" on investigators.
OL,14,FPerformance reviews set for former
OL,15,FPost Office investigators showed an
OL,16,Fincrease in the amount they were
OL,17,Fexpected to recover during the 2010s
OL,18,Ffrom 40% to 65%.
