OL,7,FMr Daily told the inquiry that the
OL,8,Fincreased figure "suggests" the
OL,9,Frecovery of cash was a "high priority"
OL,10,Ffor the Post Office ` but said it was
OL,11,Fnot viewed that way by those
OL,12,Fattempting to achieve the targets.
OL,14,FHe added that investigators were "not
OL,15,Fadequately supported" before a firm of
OL,16,Fsolicitors was brought in to advise in
OL,17,F2013.
