OL,7,FAsked why his performance targets had
OL,8,Fbeen increased, Mr Daily said: "I can
OL,9,Fonly think it was because of the
OL,10,Famount of losses the Post Office were
OL,11,Fsuffering."
OL,13,FHowever, he added that he did not
OL,14,Fbelieve the targets influenced his own
OL,15,Finvestigations.
