OL,7,FMr Daily was later asked by counsel to
OL,8,Fthe inquiry Emma Price about being
OL,9,Fgiven a bonus for his investigations.
OL,10,FResponding, he said: "I understand
OL,11,Fwhere this is coming from ` 'Were we
OL,12,Fgiven bonuses for recovering money?' `
OL,13,Fit was part of our objectives to do so.
OL,15,F"It didn't necessarily rely on a bonus
OL,16,F` we received a bonus every year
OL,17,Fregardless."
