OL,7,FExplaining how the bonus system
OL,8,Fworked, Mr Daily said: "They were
OL,9,Findividual bonuses for how you
OL,10,Fperformed over the year ` if you've
OL,11,Fperformed better than someone else.
OL,13,F"So technically you could say this
OL,14,Fwent towards (it), but if you speak to
OL,15,Findividuals within the investigation
OL,16,Fteam, the investigation managers, it
OL,17,Fwas always considered an unfair target.
