OL,7,F"Because any inquiry you did, any case
OL,8,Fyou did, all you could say to a person
OL,9,Fwas 'were you in a position to repay
OL,10,Fthe money?'
OL,12,F"If that person didn't have the money,
OL,13,Fyou couldn't get blood out of a stone."
OL,15,FMore than 700 branch managers were
OL,16,Fprosecuted by the Post Office after
OL,17,FFujitsu's faulty accounting software,
OL,18,FHorizon, made it look as though money
OL,19,Fwas missing from their branches.
