OL,7,FThe saga prompted an outcry across the
OL,8,Fcountry after it was dramatised in the
OL,9,FITV series Mr Bates v The Post Office
OL,10,Fearlier this month.
OL,12,FHundreds of subpostmasters are
OL,13,Fawaiting compensation despite the
OL,14,FGovernment announcing that those who
OL,15,Fhave had convictions quashed are
OL,16,Feligible for #600,000 payouts.
OL,18,FThe Horizon inquiry continues.
